      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_files_1" data-step-uuid="0D9CF678-EC0F-416E-B3B3-0D9BDB337F43">
    <h2 id="open_files_1" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Files</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/779/739/original/d785d61b-5fd1-42cc-b311-5554b7d27953.png" srcset="" alt="Open Files" height="384" width="710">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_89124B00-08EB-0135-42F6-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the files you want to upload to your course [1]. </p>
<p>To select a group of files, hold down the Shift key on your keyboard and click the first and last files in the group.</p>
<p>To select multiple files, hold down the Control (Windows) or Command (Mac) key on your keyboard and click each file.</p>
<p>Click the <strong>Open</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

